   <concept id="FAR_19_1306" xtrc="" class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">19.1306</ph> 
         HUBZone sole-source awards.
      </title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1235e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1269e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                   A contracting officer shall consider a contract award to a HUBZone small business concern on a sole-source basis (see <xref href="6.302-5.dita#FAR_6_302_5"
                        base="i1119624"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">6.302-5</xref>(b)(5)) before considering a small business set-aside (see <xref href="19.203.dita#FAR_19_203"
                        base="i1101696"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.203</xref> and subpart <xref href="Subpart_19.5.dita#FAR_Subpart_19_5"
                        base="i1100723"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.5</xref>), provided none of the exclusions at <xref href="19.1304.dita#FAR_19_1304"
                        base="i1099575"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.1304</xref> apply; and-</p>
               <ol id="d1235e35" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1269e28">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                         The contracting officer does not
have a reasonable expectation that offers would be received from
two or more HUBZone small business concerns;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1269e33">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                         The anticipated
price of the contract, including options, will not exceed-</p>
                     <ol id="d1235e54" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d1269e39">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              <ph rev="FAC 2025-06 October 1, 2025" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2024-001?>$8.5 million<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 19.1306 by—   a. Removing from paragraph (a)(2)(i) “$7 million” and adding “$8.5 million” in its place; and?></ph> for a requirement within the North American Industry Classification System (NAICS) codes for manufacturing; or</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d1269e44">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              <ph rev="FAC 2025-06 October 1, 2025" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2024-001?>$5.5 million<?FM MARKER [Why] b. Removing from paragraph (a)(2)(ii) “$4.5 million” and adding “$5.5 million” in its place.?></ph> for a requirement within all other NAICS codes;</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1269e49">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                         The requirement
is not currently being performed by an 8(a) participant under the
provisions of <xref href="Subpart_19.8.dita#FAR_Subpart_19_8"
                              base="i1099848"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  19.8</xref> or has
been accepted as a requirement by SBA under <xref href="Subpart_19.8.dita#FAR_Subpart_19_8"
                              base="i1099848"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  19.8</xref>;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1269e68">
                        (4) The HUBZone small business concern has been determined to be a responsible contractor with respect to performance; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1269e73">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                         Award can
be made at a fair and reasonable price.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1269e78">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> The SBA has the right to appeal the contracting officer’s decision not to make a HUBZone sole-source award (see <xref href="https://www.ecfr.gov/current/title-13/section-126.610"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">13 CFR 126.610</xref>).
               </p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
